/del phan pa 'byung zhes rab shes nas/ /u rug po ga'i ming can bu gur che/ /chung ngu'i dus nas rtag par chos 'di la/ /yid ches ldan pas rgyun du klob/ cing mchod/ rang gi go 'phang tshol zhing gsol 'debs pas/ 'thun par sbyong ba'i de dag bo bsod nams can/ /grol mdzad ston pa sangs rgyas sbrul pa gang / /thog the mur rgya ba du yun tu tshe ring zhing / /thug can rgyal po chen por 'gyur bar 'dod/ /blo ldan byang chub sems dpa' bdag po de/ slob nas se chen rgyal po'i gdan sar nga dugs/ /bdag gi yid la 'dod ba chis gyur bas/ /the tshom med par chos 'dir nges shes skyes/ /bu gu ra yi ger chos kyi mdo sde 'di/ /sngon chad gzhan gyis bsgyur ba med pas na/ /mang po'i hor rnams dad pas mchod gyur ces/ /bdag gis hor gyi skad du bsgyur pa yin/ /nga yis ji ltar bsams pa 'grub 'gyur na/ /sems can khri phrag stong phrag 'dod pa kun/ /bdag nyid ji bzhin tshem par gyur cig ces stong phrag sbar du btab nas kun la bkye/ /'di yi bsod nams drin gyi 'bras bu'i mthus/ /bdag po rgyal po dpon mo brgyud par bcas/ /yun du sku tshe ring zhing bsod nams 'phel/ /mthar thugs sangs rgyas go 'phang rnyer gyur cig rgyal khams dgra dang 'khrug bzhi ba dang / gdon dang bar chad rims med bde gyur cig/ char rlung dus 'bab mu ge med 'gyur zhing / /bdag gis smras dang bsam don 'grub bgyur cig/ bdag dang pha ma bu sogs gnyen rnams dang / /'tsho ba'i dbun dad sems can mang por bcas/ /'jig rten 'dir yang chos kyi 'dod pa chis/ /bde ba can zhing rtag par phyin gyur cig/ then li dang po'i lo 'brug gi lo zla ba bcu pa'i tshes gcig la sbar du btab pa yin/ /mdo 'di rgya gar gi yul nas rgya gar gyi ban Di ta gcig dang / thad za mtshang gis khyer te rgya'i yul du bsgyur ro/ /rgya chen po'i yul du rgyas par gyur cing gnas pa las/ rgyal po chen po'i blon po byang chub sems dpa'i rigs su byung ba dad pa dang shes rab dang / ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i gim rtse gong lun'i hu'i g-yu'i shtith'i hu u drug bo gas bskul te/ yu gur gyi bstan pa'i bdag po b+radz+nyA shrIs hor gyi skad dang yi ger bsgyur nas stong phrag gnyis sbar du btag a lin ti mur ta'i si dus yu gur gyi skad du bsgyur te/ stong phrag gcig sbar du btab nas chos kyi sgyin pa byas te/ hor dang yu gur la rgyas par byas shing / ta'i hu nyid kyang sngon chad sog po'i chos lugs 'dzin pa la/ chos 'di'i byin brlabs kyis sangs rgyas kyi chos la zhugs shing rab tu byung te/ 'di'i yon tan rnams nyams su myong bar gyur pa'o/ /slad kyis me mo glang gi lo la lo ts+tsha ba ma ti phal dang / shrI a' nanda badz+ras gud thad gi gtsug la gang du/ bod kyi skad dang yi ger bsgyur zhing zhus te gtan la phab ba'o// //
